claim.claim-text:
The apparatus according to claim 8, further comprising:
a quantizing module, configured to quantize the link adaptation update information;
wherein the sending module is further configured to send the block acknowledgment frame to the transmission opportunity holder, wherein the quantized link adaptation update information is carried in the block acknowledgment frame.
